## CompilationResult.targetOffset property

> This API is provided as a preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

An index offset to apply to BehaviorFactory target indexes when matching factories to targets.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
targetOffset: number;
```
